GET {{host}}/api/Sedinte/{{sedintaPuncte.response.body.$.id}}/Puncte
Authorization: Bearer {{loginSecretar.response.body.$.token}}

### Puncte 5. Detalii punct 1
GET {{host}}/api/Sedinte/{{sedintaPuncte.response.body.$.id}}/Puncte/1
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}

